data.description: Gorgeous single family in a highly sought neighborhood of Fountain Valley!  This home has curb appeal and is nestled on a wide quiet street interior lot with top-rated schools close to Mile Square Park, Little Saigon, beach, supermarkets, restaurants and Freeways! 4 Bedrooms (2 Up & 2 Down), 3 Baths, 2208 sqft sits on 7,200 sqft lot. Lush front yard with custom Powder Coating Metal gate leads into large private courtyard with brick walkway & beautiful foliage planters. Beautiful entry door with breeze way window and detachable screen. Huge formal living room with custom fireplace with mantel, ceiling fan, French Doors and retractable screen for easy access to the beautiful backyard. The gourmet kitchen includes granite countertops with a custom built-In granite peninsula breakfast nook, Travertine style tile backsplash, new recessed lighting, stainless appliances (gas range w/double ovens & 5 burners, dishwasher and refrigerator), new garbage disposal, new faucet, custom white shaker cabinetry with glass display panels, soft-close drawers, microwave niche, and pantry w/pull-outs. Expanded family room with open beam ceiling, wall of French windows overlooking the breathtaking resort style backyard with sparkling pool and heated spa, waterfall, covered patio, raised patio area with fire ring, block wall fencing and brick accented deck area. Conveniently downstairs master bedroom has master bathroom with designer tile floor, walk in shower with new faucet and shower head. 2nd Downstairs guest bath with walk in shower with new faucet and shower head and separate jetted soaking tub. 3rd bathroom with walk in shower with new faucet and shower head, too has a door leading to the outside of the house, great for guest to access this bathroom from the pool area. 2 Upstairs bedrooms, both have ceiling fans, 1 with Custom built-in cabinetry, shelving & desk. New HVAC, new ducting controlled from your phone, tile roof, French dual pane windows, French doors, crown molding, custom windows & door casements, Spanish pavers & hardwood floorings, open beam ceilings, tons of custom built-ins, raised panel interior doors, mirrored closets, and ceiling fans. Custom Powder Coating Metal doors for entry gates, the pool equipment, and dog run as well. Home has 6 rings camera for added safety. This private oasis property is the place for family gathering and entertainment. Don’t miss this forever home! Video https://youtu.be/Cb_6inm5akI
